# Notes:
#   - You can use either UI_* or HOMELAB_UI_* names. The runtime maps UI_* into
#     HOMELAB_UI_* if those are not already set.
#   - Per-object overrides are handled in config/ui.yml.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

